    faqs: [ { question: "Are Pionex trading bots really free?", answer: "Yes, Pionex offers 16+ trading bots at no additional cost. The platform earns revenue through trading fees (0.05%) rather than charging for bot usage." }, { question: "Which has more coins?", answer: "Binance supports 350+ coins, significantly more than Pionex's 250+ selection. Binance has the advantage for altcoin variety." }, { question: "Does Binance have trading bots?", answer: "Yes, Binance offers grid bots, DCA bots, and auto-invest. However, Pionex has more bot types and bot-building is the platform's core focus." }, { question: "Which is better for beginners?", answer: "Pionex is better for beginners who want automated trading without complexity. Binance offers more features overall but can be overwhelming." }, ],
